@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />

<h1 class="colored-text-purple">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    At <span class="colored-text-purple">LexiMotion</span>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting any information you choose to share with us. 
    This policy explains what data is collected, how it is processed, and how it is used.
</p>

<h3>1. Data Collection</h3>
<ul>
    <li>LexiMotion may collect text data provided directly by users (e.g., Reddit post or comment links submitted for analysis).</li>
    <li>When using automated data gathering (e.g., research mode), the system may collect publicly available social media content such as Reddit posts or comments.</li>
    <li>No personally identifiable information (PII) is required to use LexiMotion.</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Data Usage</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Submitted text data is processed to detect emotions, negations, and sarcasm.</li>
    <li>Analysis results may be stored in a PostgreSQL database for visualization and research purposes.</li>
    <li>Data is used solely for sentiment and emotion analysis and is not sold, shared, or used for advertising.</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Data Storage & Security</h3>
<ul>
    <li>All processed data is stored securely in PostgreSQL databases under controlled access.</li>
    <li>Sensitive or personal user input is not logged unless explicitly permitted for research or testing.</li>
    <li>We apply industry-standard security practices to safeguard stored data.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. User Control</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Users control what data they submit for analysis (e.g., by providing a link or text).</li>
    <li>If a user does not want their content processed, they should not provide links or text to the system.</li>
    <li>Data can be deleted upon request during research or testing phases.</li>
</ul>

<h3>5. Research Context</h3>
<ul>
    <li>LexiMotion is a personal project focused on natural language processing, emotion detection, and sentiment analysis.</li>
    <li>The system is not a commercial product and is intended for research, demonstration, and educational purposes only.</li>
</ul>

<h3>6. Contact</h3>
<p>
    For questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact the developer at 
    <a href="mailto:emjayprojas@gmail.com">emjayprojas@gmail.com</a>.
</p>

<p><em>Last updated: September 10, 2025</em></p>
